diagrams.mermaid:
flowchart TD
  Start([新診斷子宮頸癌]) --> Hist{病理組織型?}
  Hist -->|NECC 神經內分泌| Special1[特殊組織型 track:<br>不適用 fertility-sparing<br>系統化療為主]
  Hist -->|Gastric-type adeno| Special2[特殊組織型 track:<br>不適用 conservative surgery<br>走 standard radical]
  Hist -->|鱗狀/一般腺/adenosquamous| Stage{FIGO 分期}

  Stage --> S_IA1[IA1]
  Stage --> S_IA2[IA2 / IB1]
  Stage --> S_IB2[IB2<br>2-4cm]
  Stage --> S_IB3[IB3 / IIA2<br>≥4cm]
  Stage --> S_IIB[IIB-IVA<br>locally advanced]
  Stage --> S_IVB[IVB<br>distant metastasis]

  S_IA1 --> IA1_dec{LVSI?}
  IA1_dec -->|negative| IA1_neg[Conization 切緣陰性<br>or Type A hyst]
  IA1_dec -->|positive| IA1_pos[Type A hyst<br>+ SLN/pelvic LND]

  S_IA2 --> IA2_dec{符合 NCCN 保守手術標準?<br>無 LVSI + 切緣陰性 + 鱗狀/一般腺<br>+ ≤2cm + depth <10mm}
  IA2_dec -->|符合| TypeA[Type A hyst<br>+ SLN/LND]
  IA2_dec -->|不符| ModRad[Modified radical hyst<br>+ pelvic LND ± SLN<br>IB1: open 首選 per LACC]
  IA2_dec -->|想保留生育| Trach1[Radical trachelectomy<br>+ LND ≤2cm]

  S_IB2 --> IB2_branch{選擇路徑}
  IB2_branch --> IB2_surg[Radical hyst<br>+ LND ± para-aortic]
  IB2_branch --> IB2_ccrt[Definitive CCRT]
  IB2_branch -->|想保留生育| Trach2[Abdominal radical<br>trachelectomy + LND<br>經篩選,非絕對禁忌]

  S_IB3 --> CCRT[Definitive CCRT<br>cisplatin weekly<br>+ EBRT + IGBT brachy]
  CCRT --> INTERLACE_opt[+ INTERLACE 前導化療<br>carbo+paclitaxel × 6 wk<br>NCCN 新增選項]
  CCRT --> CompHyst[CCRT 後殘餘 / 無 IGBT<br>→ selective completion hyst<br>cat 3]

  S_IIB --> CCRT2[Definitive CCRT + IGBT]
  CCRT2 --> Pembro[KEYNOTE-A18:<br>+ Pembrolizumab + 維持]
  Pembro --> Pembro_cat{FIGO 2014 vs 2018?}
  Pembro_cat -->|2014 IIIA-IVA| Cat1[Category 1]
  Pembro_cat -->|2018 純 IIIC LN-defined| Cat2B[Category 2B]
  CCRT2 --> INTERLACE2[INTERLACE 前導化療<br>適用 IIB-IVA]

  S_IVB --> Sys[Systemic 第一線:<br>cisplatin/carbo + paclitaxel<br>+ bevacizumab<br>+ Pembrolizumab CPS≥1<br>KEYNOTE-826]

  classDef special fill:#fdf8e8,stroke:#b8543a,stroke-width:2px;
  class Special1,Special2 special;
  classDef stage fill:#e8f0e0,stroke:#5a7a4a;
  class S_IA1,S_IA2,S_IB2,S_IB3,S_IIB,S_IVB stage;
  classDef good fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class Cat1 good;

flowchart TD
  PostSurg([Radical hysterectomy 術後<br>病理 review]) --> PathRisk{病理風險評估}

  PathRisk -->|高度風險 任一| HighRisk[Peters criteria:<br>• Positive LN<br>• Parametrial invasion<br>• Positive surgical margin]
  HighRisk --> CCRT_adj[Adjuvant CCRT<br>cisplatin + pelvic RT<br>HR 0.54 vs RT alone<br>GOG-109 基礎]

  PathRisk -->|中度風險 符合組合| MedRisk[Sedlis criteria:<br>LVSI + 侵犯深度 + 腫瘤大小<br>四種組合任一]
  MedRisk --> RT_adj[Adjuvant pelvic RT<br>HR 0.53 vs observation<br>GOG-92 基礎]

  PathRisk -->|無上述風險| LowRisk[Observation]

  classDef high fill:#f8d7da,stroke:#c0392b;
  class HighRisk,CCRT_adj high;
  classDef med fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class MedRisk,RT_adj med;
  classDef low fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class LowRisk low;

flowchart TD
  Recur([Persistent / recurrent / metastatic]) --> CPS{PD-L1 CPS}

  CPS -->|CPS ≥ 1| L1A[第一線 KEYNOTE-826:<br>cisplatin/carbo + paclitaxel<br>+ bevacizumab<br>+ Pembrolizumab<br>Category 1]

  CPS -->|CPS < 1<br>或不可測| L1B[第一線 GOG-240:<br>cisplatin/carbo + paclitaxel<br>+ bevacizumab<br>無 pembro]

  L1A -->|progression| L2_dec{第二線選擇}
  L1B -->|progression| L2_dec

  L2_dec -->|未用過 IO| Cemip[Cemiplimab<br>EMPOWER-Cervical 1<br>OS 12.0 vs 8.5 月]
  L2_dec -->|已用過 IO| Chemo2[二線化療<br>topotecan / pemetrexed<br>vinorelbine / gemcitabine]

  Cemip -->|progression| Later[後線: Tisotumab vedotin<br>innovaTV 204/301<br>ORR 24%]
  Chemo2 -->|progression| Later

  classDef first fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class L1A,L1B first;
  classDef second fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class Cemip,Chemo2 second;
  classDef last fill:#f8d7da,stroke:#c0392b;
  class Later last;
